text: Nezha Alaoui is a Moroccan-born entrepreneur and founder of the Mayshad brand. She is also the founder of the Mayshad Foundation, a non-profit organization for youth and women's development. == References == == Other websites == * Mayshad Group website * Mayshad Foundation website * Join Mayshad Category:Moroccan people Category:1982 births Category:Living people
